"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/794329","Department of Health","false","2017-12-01","<p>Freestyle Libre has been approved for reimbursement on National Health Service prescription from 1 November through listing in Part IX of the Drug Tariff. The Drug Tariff is a price list that covers England and Wales, and the listing of a medical device in the Tariff should not be interpreted as a recommendation to prescribe a particular product. Patients will need to discuss the ongoing management of their condition with their healthcare professional and consider whether flash glucose monitoring is suitable for them.</p>","Winchester","Steve Brine","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/794329/answer",,,,,,"2017-12-01T13:00:42.627Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/794329/answer","Biography information for Steve Brine","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/794329/answer",,,,,"17","Health","Health","2017-11-23","Diabetes: Medical Equipment","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Health, if he will take steps to ensure that the FreeStyle Libre Flash Glucose Monitoring system is accessible to all diabetes patients","false","Biography information for Laura Smith","Crewe and Nantwich","Laura Smith","115302"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/794330","Cabinet Office","false","2017-11-28","<p>It is the responsibility of the Contracting Authority to ensure it is compliant with EU procurement legislation during any procurement process. Contracting Authorities will assess the risk of appointing any given supplier, and this will be tailored to the requirements of the specific procurement.</p>","Romsey and Southampton North","Caroline Nokes","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/794330/answer",,,,,"115304","2017-11-28T15:42:52.993Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/794330/answer","Biography information for Caroline Nokes","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/794330/answer",,,,,"53","Cabinet Office","Cabinet Office","2017-11-23","Carillion","1","House of Commons","To ask the Minister for the Cabinet Office, what risk was identified during the procurement process that identified Carillion as a service delivery contractor to (a) the operation of public services and (b) value for money of the potential effect of Carillion plc going into administration.","false","Biography information for Jon Trickett","Hemsworth","Jon Trickett","115303"
